Bing wallpaper of the day will be downloaded and setted.
Wallpaper will be updated at every login.
The wallpaper will be saved to the choosen directory.
You can also preview the wallpapers on the directory by double cliccking on them.
The directory size limit field allo you to set a maxim directory size in MegaBytes. Please enter only integer numbers and a value smaller then 1000 Mb. If you set non integer or a value bigger then 1000, the size limit will be disabled
